OL,3,CPaignton and Newquay Zoos announce
OL,4,Credundancies as running costs hit #1m
OL,5,Ca month
OL,7,FA number of redundancies have been
OL,8,Fannounced at Paignton Zoo in Devon and
OL,9,FNewquay Zoo in Cornwall.
OL,11,FBoth are run by the Wild Planet Trust,
OL,12,Fwhich is blaming what it calls a
OL,13,Fseries of crippling challenges for the
OL,14,Fannouncement.
OL,16,FA special rescue package has been put
OL,17,Ftogether to ensure the future
OL,18,Fviability of both zoos and the trust
OL,19,Fsays the welfare and safety of the
OL,20,Fanimals remains their top priority.
