OL,3,CPaignton and Newquay Zoos announce
OL,4,Credundancies as running costs hit #1m
OL,5,Ca month
OL,7,FOperational costs for both zoos now
OL,8,Famount to #1 million per month, which
OL,9,Fthe trust says means they have to take
OL,10,Fcost-cutting measures, including staff
OL,11,Fredundancies.
OL,13,FStephen Kings, interim Executive Chair
OL,14,Fof the Trust, stated: "Unfortunately,
OL,15,Fthe combination of COVID-19, Avian
OL,16,FInfluenza, and the cost-of-living
OL,17,Fcrisis has resulted in fewer visitors
OL,18,Fto our zoos over the past few years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
