OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F436A1721307244
OL,3,CPaignton and Newquay Zoos announce
OL,4,Credundancies as running costs hit #1m
OL,5,Ca month
OL,7,F"It is often forgotten that we are a
OL,8,Fcharity purely funded by our
OL,9,Fsupporters, members and visitors.
OL,11,F"Therefore this has forced the Trust
OL,12,Fto cut costs, which inevitably means
OL,13,Fredundancies.
OL,15,F"This decision has not been taken
OL,16,Flightly. We consider ourselves a
OL,17,Ffamily at the zoo, but we have no
OL,18,Foption but to review our staff and
OL,19,Foperating costs."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
