OL,3,CPaignton and Newquay Zoos announce
OL,4,Credundancies as running costs hit #1m
OL,5,Ca month
OL,7,FThe Trust still owes more than #1
OL,8,Fmillion to the government for a loan
OL,9,Ftaken during the COVID-19 pandemic
OL,10,Fwhen zoos were forced to close down.
OL,12,FAdditionally, Avian Influenza resulted
OL,13,Fin more than #1 million in lost
OL,14,Frevenue in 2022, and the cost-of-
OL,15,Fliving crisis has further decreased
OL,16,Fvisitor numbers and income.
OL,18,FMr Kings added: "The health and
OL,19,Fwelfare of our animals is our number
OL,20,Fone priority.
