OL,3,CPaignton and Newquay Zoos announce
OL,4,Credundancies as running costs hit #1m
OL,5,Ca month
OL,7,F"We are working specifically to raise
OL,8,Fcapital funding to refurbish the large
OL,9,Fmammal house, rehouse the baboons,
OL,10,Freopen the currently closed Croc Swamp
OL,11,Fat Paignton, to extend old buildings
OL,12,Fto provide better accommodation for
OL,13,Fanimals, develop the penguin pool, and
OL,14,Fremove the overgrown maze at Newquay.
OL,16,F"We have many other improvement plans
OL,17,Fin place for future developments so
OL,18,Ftherefore need the support of everyone
OL,19,Fwho loves our zoos."
